{"title":"Podcast #079 – Triton Bikes’ Amazing Escape from Russia","link":"https://bikerumor.com/podcast-079-triton-cycles-amazing-escape-from-russia/","date":1680287908000,"content":"<p>I think, at some level, we all crave adventure. It’s why the Zombie Apocalypse genre is so popular. What would we do if we had to drop everything and just… escape. Start fresh.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Well, for many folks around the world, it’s not a fantasy. It’s why we have so many people trying to migrate into the USA and most of Europe They’re trying to escape a desperate if not downright dangerous situation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And that’s where we pick up in this episode, bringing it close to home with my friend Dmitry Nechaev (neeh-chive). He’s the founder of <a href=\"https://triton-bikes.com/en/triton-groont-en/\" target=\"_blank\">Triton Bike</a>, which, up until very recently, was based in Russia and making gorgeous custom titanium bicycles.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Everything changed for him when Russia invaded Ukraine, and his story about how he and his family got out, and how he eventually relocated the business, his employees, and equipment to Portugal is <em>WILD!</em></p>\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n<p>From sneaking parts out to having friends and co-workers ride for days to cross by bicycle at remote border stations, he has some stories to tell. We talk about why he’s living in Israel but re-launching in Portugal, and, toward the end, we talk about how they’re rebuilding the brand getting ready to build their first bikes in their new factory.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"649\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike-800x649.jpg\" alt=\"triton cycles van with NAHBS road bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike-800x649.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike-297x241.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike-120x97.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike-768x623.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike-1536x1247.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-nahbs-bike.jpg 1800w\" /></a><figcaption>Dmitry with his road bike and new delivery van.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s a long one, but stay tuned at the end for a recap of a few other things we discussed after I stopped recording. Scroll below for some photos from his journey and setting up their new factory.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8-800x1067.jpg\" alt=\"triton cycles driving out of russia\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8-225x300.jpg 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8-90x120.jpg 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-8.jpg 1400w\" /></a><figcaption>Driving out of Russia.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7-800x1067.jpg\" alt=\"Dmitrys land rover\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7-225x300.jpg 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7-90x120.jpg 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7-1536x2048.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-7.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Dmitry’s Land Rover, which a friend drove out of Russia for him, with his bike inside</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6-800x1067.jpg\" alt=\"land rover in front of eiffel tower\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6-225x300.jpg 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6-90x120.jpg 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-6.jpg 1400w\" /></a><figcaption>Sights along the way from picking up his truck north of Russia, heading to Portugal.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"897\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5-800x897.jpg\" alt=\"welcome to portugal sign\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5-800x897.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5-268x300.jpg 268w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5-107x120.jpg 107w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5-768x861.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5-1371x1536.jpg 1371w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-5.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4-800x600.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-4.jpg 1800w\" /></a><figcaption>The new Triton Cycles HQ and factory in Portugal.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-2.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"700\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-2-800x700.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-2-800x700.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-2-297x260.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-2-120x105.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-2-768x672.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-2.jpg 1462w\" /></a><figcaption>Loading in the new machines.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1-800x600.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-1.jpg 1800w\" /></a><figcaption>The beginnings of a new Triton Cycles production line.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3-800x350.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3-800x350.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3-297x130.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3-120x52.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3-768x336.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3-1536x672.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-escape-to-portugal-3-2048x896.jpg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Some of Triton Cycles’ fixtures they were able to get out of Russia.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-groont-gravel-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"521\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-groont-gravel-bike-800x521.jpg\" alt=\"triton cycles groont titanium gravel bike, shot before the exodus.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-groont-gravel-bike-800x521.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-groont-gravel-bike-297x193.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-groont-gravel-bike-120x78.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-groont-gravel-bike-768x500.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/triton-cycles-groont-gravel-bike.jpg 1440w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Huge thanks to Dmitry for sharing his story with us, and if you’re looking for a new bike, please check them out and point some friends their way, it’ll help them rebuild the business. Find them at <a href=\"https://triton-bikes.com/en/triton-groont-en/\" target=\"_blank\">Triton-Bikes.com</a>. Follow on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tritonbikes/\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tritonbikes/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>, too!</p>\n\n\